## Introduction to Battle Pass
HI3 Battle Pass rewards are very different from Honkai Star Rail and Genshin Impact. The biggest differences are:



1. You earn a currency called <span class="text-pink-300">Immutable Crystallum</span> which can be used to purchase past S-rank characters and equipment released 3+ years ago.
2. If you purchase the paid tier, you'll receive additional Crystallum and gain access to more recent S-rank characters and equipment from the past 1â€“2 years.

