## BP Tiers
There are three tiers - <span class="text-teal-300">Vanguard</span> (Free), <span class="text-orange-300">Knight</span> (~10 USD), and <span class="text-red-300">Paladin</span> (~20 USD). 


<div class="flex items-center justify-center text-orange-300 ">
  <img src="https://i.imgur.com/WAXr9VU.png" alt="Icon" class="w-[600px] h-auto rounded-lg" />
</div>

### Crystallum Income Per Patch
- Vanguard: 5
- Knight: 18
- Paladin: 24


### Some notable rewards for the paid tier
- Knight / Paladin BP unlocks the ability to purchase S-rank character and equipment from 1-2 years ago.
- Knight / Paladin BP gives fragments for the featured S-rank. Knight 10 frags, Paladin 10+20 = 30 frags.
- Paladin BP gives Wafer Stabilizer and Dataflow, used to fine-tune stigma affix stats. This is useful for competitive players.
- Cosmetic: Knight BP gives an outfit / outfit box, Paladin BP gives a ribbon.





