### Should You Get Knight / Paladin For This Shop?

If you can afford it, yeah definitely. Part 2 characters all have their niche as both dps and support, and this shop is how you can quickly get the older Part 2 characters.

> Why don't I just get these characters from supplies?

If you haven't noticed, NOT ALL CHARACTERS ARE IN BATTLESUIT SUPPLY - ONLY THE RECENT ONES. These characters are in Battle Pass for a reason - they will no longer appear in regular supplies.

---

### Should I get THIS or THAT?

Refer to [each valk guide page](/valk) for more info. But general answer for most cases: Get Part 2 valk first. If all the sets are for Part 2 valk, then get the latest valk.

---

### How the shop works
- In each version, BP Works adds a set of S-rank character and her equipment.
- Every set lasts for 3 versions.
- The shop has 3 sets: set from current patch and previous two patches. Since the shop was only added last patch, v8.3 will only have the v8.2 and v8.3 S-rank set.
- Purchasing Knight or Paladin BP will allow you to purchase all 3 sets that are available in that version. In the next version, if you don't buy Knight or Paladin BP, you cannot purchase the content of the new set added in that version, but you can still purchase the set from the previous 2 versions.

