## Reserve Works Shop

Reserve Works Shop has all S-rank characters and most equipment from over 3 years ago. Currently, the content of the shop is up until <span class="text-pink-300"> Herrscher of Origin patch (v6.4) </span>.

The developers have stated that this shop will be updated gradually over time.

![BP Equipment](https://i.imgur.com/tNpwwOy.png)

<br/>






### Best Item to Get

#### 1. BP Works Item
Reminder: Items in Reserve Works uses **the same currency** as BP Works Shop. It is always better to purchase item in BP Works since they are newer.

---

#### 2. Divine Keys

<div class="flex items-center justify-center text-orange-300 ">
  <img src="https://i.imgur.com/ayypL15.png" alt="Icon" class="w-[700px] h-auto rounded-lg" />
</div>

Divine Keys give global +10 ATK for all characters. When these stack up, they can give a significant damage increase, equal to having a second weapon on your valk.

However, do note that some Divine Keys have been given for free in the past, and may be available in major spending event (happens twice a year). Only get the Divine Keys above from BP if you can't wait that long.

---

#### 3. Meta Character


<div class="flex items-center justify-center text-orange-300 ">
  <img src="https://i.imgur.com/MLHZ782.png" alt="Icon" class="h-[250px] w-auto rounded-lg" />
</div>

Herrscher of Human (HoH) and Herrscher of Origin (HoO) are the only meta characters in the shop. If you have not maxed their ranks yet, then you can consider getting the stamps from this shop.

**Regarding buying battlesuit for F2P** <br/>
For F2P, 24 Crystallum cost is VERY EXPENSIVE. It is equal to 5 patches worth of Crystallum, that is almost a year worth! 

**For new players that can afford it** <br/>
HoH battlesuit is available in starter B-chip pack. Save your Crystallum and get HoH from the pack instead.

**Note**<br/> 
For HoH: Only get the stamps, don't get her equipment. She uses a different set for Part 2. [Please go to Herrscher of Human guide page to learn more.](/valk/hoh)

---

#### 4. Save

Everything else in the Reserve Works shop is outdated. Save your crystallum for BP Works Shop item, or wait for a better item that might get added to the Reserve Works shop in the future.